<span id="freeTextContainer13117867416301516619">It&apos;s like every sentence you have to hack out of the rockface, it takes forever to read the thing, it&apos;s like some kind of titanic struggle you have with it, but when you finally do finish the damn thing you feel like you&apos;ve been through some kind of... experience. Not sure I need another going over by E Annie Proulx, but this one was memorable.<br/> <br/>The author : &quot;Say my name!&quot;<br/>PB : &quot;Ooof, E Annie!&quot;<br/>Pow, kick, bash.<br/>The author : &quot;Say my name!&quot;<br/>PB : &quot;Cough - I already said it - E Annie Proulx! <b>E ANNIE PROU</b></span>
