              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8642187825714696277">Loved this book for the same reasons I&apos;ve cared about all her books. One thing comes back time and again-Proulx&apos;s research and attention to detail. No one else I&apos;ve read is as good at drilling down on a subject as she is (trapping techniques in this book, for example). She must love research.</span>
  <span id="freeText8642187825714696277" style="display:none">Loved this book for the same reasons I've cared about all her books. One thing comes back time and again-Proulx's research and attention to detail. No one else I've read is as good at drilling down on a subject as she is (trapping techniques in this book, for example). She must love research.</span>
